Problem Description
3) Write a Java program to create an abstract class Type with an abstract method reverse(). Create subclasses StringType & IntegerType that
Extend the Type class & override the reverse() method to reverse the given string & reverse the digits.

Examples
Example 1
Input:
hello
1234
Output:
Reversed String: olleh
Reversed Integer Digits: 4321
Important Note
Your code must be able to print the sample output from the provided sample input. However, your solution also runs against multiple hidden test cases. You must pass these hidden test cases to fully solve the problem.

Limits
Memory Limit: 1 MB
Time Limit: 60 m
//
Solution
import java. Util.*;

public class TypeReverseApp{
    public static void main(String[] args){
